        #   +----+-------------+-------+-------+---------------+---------+---------+-------+------+-------------+
        #   |  1 | SIMPLE      | users | const | PRIMARY       | PRIMARY | 4       | const |    1 |             |
        #   |  1 | SIMPLE      | posts | ALL   | NULL          | NULL    | NULL    | NULL  |    1 | Using where |
        #   +----+-------------+-------+-------+---------------+---------+---------+-------+------+-------------+
        #   2 rows in set (0.00 sec)
